Text: Re OSPBC Drafting Committee Meeting Teleconferencing Dec I will be unable to make tomorrows meeting Ill call you Wed or Thurs to discuss the outcome Larry Original Message From Dave Butters To Sent Tuesday December PM Subject OSPBC Drafting Committee Meeting Teleconferencing Dec If you are involved with the Drafting Committee and intend to call in for tomorrows meeting please let me or my assistant Elaine Bullard x know soonest We are arranging to have a callin number and password which will be sent to those calling in later today Thanks Dave Butters x Office email To unsubscribe from this group send an email to eGroups Sponsor eGroups eLerts Its Easy Its Fun Best of All its Free To unsubscribe from this group send an email to
